at the wall clock, my foot got a brain on its own and started tapping.\r\nTen minutes before ending, my pen was dancing in my hand. And finally, “for\r\nyour assignment, do a research about different lenses,” the bell rang.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I reached for my bag, but it wasn’t there, then I suddenly\r\nthink, why am I looking for my bag? Then, leave it. Then, but my things? Then,\r\ndo I have a bag? That’s great. Now, where is it?<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I give up and made it in the hallway. Jack was leaning near\r\nthe gate, looking at his flip phone in his left hand, a book about business on\r\nthe other.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“I’ll walk you on your house,” he said looking on the floor,\r\nhis phone was in his ears when I was in front of him.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“What was that? Why are you—?”<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“Later.”<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I stop walking. Look at him. His eyes meet mine.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“Come on,” he said, smiling at me this time, and leading the\r\nway.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It was thirty minutes journey back home. And ninety-nine\r\npercent of it filled with silence. I wanted to break it. I wanted to ask more\r\nabout those ‘smoke thingy,\' made him talk, grab him, pushed him, annoy him. Or\r\nanything, just to make him noisy, he wasn’t like this. Never silent, or sad.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">He led me like he’d been in my place before, he never did. I\r\ndid nothing but follow him, looking at smokes coming from his foot.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">We reached my house, and something was off the order,\r\neverything. Inside and out, people are coming. From the windows, I can see it\r\ninside was filled with smoke.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I saw my brother and sister; mother and father were even\r\nthere, talking with our visitors. They are all wearing black.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sister spotted us first, tugged brother’s sleeve, and meet\r\nus before we enter the gate. But like this morning, they ignored me and\r\nentertained only Jack. “I want to see him,” Jack said to them.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">They nodded and lead us inside, which added to my confusion.\r\nIn the living room, the couch was pushed in the side. White flowers are\r\neverywhere. And in the middle, was a white coffin with a burning candle on each\r\nside.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">My head was spinning, I look for my sister and brother for\r\nan explanation, but they are still ignoring me. Who’s dead? I saw mother and\r\nfather when we arrived.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I wanted to peek, but Jack spoke. “No don’t.”<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">I looked at him, but his phone was in his ears again, but he\r\nwas looking straight into my eyes. “Not until I said you this.”<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">My brother and sister look at each other, looked at him, and\r\nin my direction. Their faces were confused. We stopped in the doorway, blocking\r\nthe entrance.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“I was grateful to we have met,” Jack continued still\r\nlooking at me, his voice was soft and silent that only me and my siblings can\r\nhear. Tears started to leak from his eyes. He was speaking to me, but why the\r\nphone? Why the tears? My brother pats him in the back as they are being called,\r\nJack nodded. They still ignored me.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“I’m sorry I wasn’t able to protect you until the last,”\r\nJack choked and walked for the coffin. His hand on my back.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">No! Five steps and I saw who’s inside.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">My twin, sleeping peacefully, inside the coffin. His\r\ninnocent face reflecting how his hard life could be. His bangs were combed\r\nhiding his forehead.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Now I understand. Jack’s changing mood. My gloomy siblings.\r\nThe nightmare. Smokes. My missing golden tentacles.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Now I know why Jack never saw his brother’s golden essence\r\nuntil we meet. Now I know the reason why, in the first place, suddenly, I was\r\nwearing a string necklace with a cold bullet tied in the center when I woke up\r\nlast night.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Now I know that Jack never really lied to me.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It was all because my twin chose to sleep inside a coffin.\r\nIt was all because I don’t have a twin.<o:p></o:p></p>', 1),
(2, 'Impostor', 'impostor', '2021-04-30 11:40:50', 1, 'impostor.jpg', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Marami na ang nagbago,</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Marami na ang nasira,</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sa patuloy na pag-agos ng buhay; Kasalanan ang pagiging totoo Kasalanan ang maging malaya.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sa tila laro na aming ginagampanan; pagkatao ang siyang nakataya Kanino kakampi?</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Kailangan ba lagi magpaubaya?</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">O, ibabaling muli sa iba ang sisi?</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sa kulay ng balat na tila ba raw nagbabagang uling,</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sa mala bola at poste raw na hugis ng katawan.</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Itsura mo raw na mababa pa raw ang halaga sa singsing.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sinong paniniwalaan mo?</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Walang laro, na bobolahin kalang para manalo</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Ma-subtract man ang points mo sa langit</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Dagdagan mo ang points sa kargada; kung paano mananalo</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Ikaw lang naman ang patuloy na tumatawid sa kaisipan na wala kang kwenta Kaisipan na sinasabing wala ka naman ibubuga</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Mga salitang galing lang naman sa iba ngunit pilit na sinasaksak diretso sa kaluluwa</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Porke ba, sila ay may nagkikinangan na mga mukha at magandang katawan, sila ay nakakahigit na? Ako\'y iyong pinapatawa</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Bakit tila iniisip mo ito ay isang kompetensiya?</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Wag ka magtago sa sapin na kinukulong ka sa karma</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sino ba ang impostor?</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">\'Wag mo ako ituro</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Ako ang ikaw na tila hinayaan mo\'ng maagos palayo sa dagat</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Ikaw ang ako na akala mo kaya mo mag-isa hanggang dulo</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">At, ikaw ang impostor na patuloy na nagiging palaisipan sakin.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Impostor ko..</span><br style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Hindi mo ba ako kayang lubayan?</span><br></p>', 2),
